run(sql="
with cte as(
    select * from(
        select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) as date, guid, sessionId, utmTerm
        from `last125Days(appLaunch)` 
        where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))>='2023-04-01'
        union 
        select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000)) as date, firstGuid as guid, sessionId, utmTerm
        from `last125Days(sessionSummary)` 
        where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000))>='2023-04-01'
    ) order by guid
)

select date, count (distinct case when lower(utmTerm) like '%790_179_Web_WAP_DPA%' then sessionId end) as visits
from cte 
group by date 
order by date desc

",1000)
